# 🚀 QUICK PATH FIX - AI Agent Reference

## 🔥 **Emergency One-Liner Fix**
```bash
# Complete fix for most common issues
filename="your_file.mdc"
sed -i '' -e 's/@\([^\.]*\.mdc\)/[\1]/g' -e 's/\/\.\/\/g' -e 's/\.\/.cursor\/.cursor\/g' -e 's/]\(\.\([^)]*\.mdc\))/](.cursor\/rules\/01__AI-RUN\2)/g' -e 's/))/)/g' "$filename"
```

## 🔍 **Quick Diagnostic**
```bash
grep -E "@.*\.mdc|/\./|mdc:" filename.mdc
```

## ✅ **Quick Verification**
```bash
grep -c "@\|/\.\/" filename.mdc || echo "✅ PATHS CLEAN"
```

## 🎯 **Most Common Fixes**

| Problem | Command |
|---------|---------|
| `@file.mdc` | `sed -i '' 's/@\([^\.]*\.mdc\)/[\1]/g' file.mdc` |
| `/` paths | `sed -i '' 's/\/\.\/\/g' file.mdc` |
| `mdc:` corruption | `sed -i '' 's/mdc:/.\/g' file.mdc` |
| Double `))` | `sed -i '' 's/))/)/g' file.mdc` |

## 🛡️ **Safety Check**
```bash
# Always backup first
cp filename.mdc filename.mdc.backup

# Test file existence after fix
cd workspace_root && ls rules/01__AI-RUN/*.mdc
```

